org.openehealth.ipf.platform.camel.flow

Class PlatformPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openehealth.ipf.platform.camel.flow.PlatformPacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PlatformPacket
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A serializable data container for Exchange content. The data contained in this packet are sufficient to re-create an Exchange and replay it with the flow manager.
    Author:
    Martin Krasser
